videos.description: Baylor's Mark Vital misses from close range then gets the steal and jams it home on the other end.
videos.headline: Vital makes up for missed basket with fast-break dunk for Bears

videos.description: Washington big man Isaiah Stewart makes an amazing block and the ball goes in the basket off the defection, but is waived off for basket interference by Baylor.

tracking.trackingName: CBB_One Play (Stewart gets block but Clark basket waived off by interference) 2019/11/08 ESHEETS

videos.headline: Stewart gets block but Clark basket waived off by interference

videos.description: Isaiah Stewart's turnaround floater in the paint scores the go-ahead basket for Washington in a comeback win over Baylor.
videos.headline: Freshman Stewart comes up clutch for UW
